程序包 algonquin.cst2335.finalproject.trivia

类 Grade

java.lang.Object
algonquin.cst2335.finalproject.trivia.Grade
public class Grade extends Object
Represents a Grade entity for the Trivia game. This class is used to store information about a player's grade in a specific category and question number.
